{
  "stem": "19939.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know exactly, if this was already the ghetto, or not yet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe they made this ghetto after this action, I think, after.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now I-- also my mother's father lived with us at the time, the grandfather.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because he was then, his wife died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was what was so poignant, you know, talking about-- about not resisting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was no way to resist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So came the day, it was a announcement-- this was-- I guess it was already in '42 or '41.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Probably it must have been '42.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, must have been '42.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In German they had-- they announced that everybody has to stay home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- not to go out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they brought then people, then my grandmother, right, the one that I was with them when the Germans moved in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in the beginning, I was still able to go and visit to my-- or maybe not during the war, in the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyhow, they surrounded the whole thing, and nobody was allowed to-- it was that even nobody was allowed to leave, all-- all the night.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were staying the following day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They-- so we were sitting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't know if we've going to live or not, from the next day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because this has already started, this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They brought people, Jews, with wagons, with horses, with the carriages from the neighboring smaller town and villages to this Debica.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my father came from this other, from [INAUDIBLE], and many of his friends, relatives, came.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they all came, you know-- I am a little mixed up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Maybe this was already after the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Yeah, they brought everybody in, right, from the surrounding things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my grandmother came home, came and she was all bent.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
